{"tid":1527091,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"全部人入黎推  聽日三罷點解可以完全無人講","createTime":"2019-09-01T08:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T00:35:34.000Z","uid":69380,"like":117,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef26c9f3cf40659fac064214049aed4d3f95096","tid":1527091,"uid":69380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"九月二 三 連續兩日三罷 <br />\n我地唔做多啲全社會一齊參與對政府 對經濟有大傷害既抗爭運動出黎 只會比政府比狗有更多機會做出 721 831既恐襲事件出黎<br />\n我明白大家都好憤怒 但我地更加唔可以白白浪費手足既付出<br />\n聽日 後日 三罷 不合作運動 全民一齊癱瘓香港 <br />\n既然呢個社會呢個政府咁鍾意講經濟 我地都打佢經濟<br />\n香港無未來 我地又何來未來?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"a28df04db50d64d4448c862cb9ea5651e9aa036e","tid":1527091,"uid":263058,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:53:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68bac8ec4386c24a76e4f38f001a884e6c383756","tid":1527091,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2185ec2c8624f9389213fbc9e8a482f0d38e48a1","tid":1527091,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:55:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5efc2d9255f3cc75f2a5ccbdaf144c3712fad424","tid":1527091,"uid":272119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca25d4267df41ebee8a80ff843776bafeb097893","tid":1527091,"uid":315880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37c1e0ed71e3e4c5d7d7fc68a56e96789aa7bc39","tid":1527091,"uid":44086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"推呀聽日三罷！！！"},{"pid":"cc1d2203c194d652cc9652d27807caea995c91a0","tid":1527091,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:58:42.000Z","